#

Arugula and Chickpea Salad

10 min
$8
220 kcal
Difficulty: 10%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

Dairy (if adding feta)

Dietary Tags:

VegetarianGluten-FreeNut-Free

Cuisine:

Mediterranean

Course:

Main or Side Salad

Tags:

SaladHealthyQuickVegetarian

Description

A fresh and nutritious salad packed with protein and flavor, perfect for a quick meal!

Ingredients

  • arugula: 4 cups
  • canned chickpeas: 1 can (15 oz)
  • cherry tomatoes: 1 cup
  • cucumber: 1 medium
  • red onion: 1/4 medium
  • feta cheese: 1/2 cup (optional)
  • olive oil: 2 tablespoons
  • lemon juice: 2 tablespoons
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
